    "Advanced techniques, such as those introduced in [92], incorporate continuous prompts at each layer rather than solely at the input layer, boosting performance in natural language understanding tasks.",
    "Additionally, memory efficiency is also a critical topic.",
    "Models can first be quantized or decomposed into low-precision data types, and only the LoRAs corresponding to specific downstream tasks are tuned [93].",
    "In [94], scalar vectors resulting from decomposition are also updated.",
    "Our method is greatly inspired by LoRA, thanks to its scalability."
